cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.NE

The paper deals with audio event detection using a convolutional recurrent neural network, which is a combination of computer vision and natural language processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.SI (Speech and Natural Language Processing), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
